Step 1: download mongo db
URL:  https://www.mongodb.com/try/download/community
For window: https://fastdl.mongodb.org/windows/mongodb-windows-x86_64-6.0.6-signed.msi

Step 2: Install mongo db. 
click on the mongodb-windows-x86_64-6.0.6-signed.msi and accept the term and condition and select complete option and proceed.
Once the installation is then close the welcome-compass popup.

step 3: add the path in the system environment variable
